+- `T-214-02`: duplicate of `T-214-01`. No separate code change.
+- `T-214-03`: obsolete. Outdated diff hunk; legacy behavior was not restored.
+- `T-214-04`: actionable. Added regression coverage in `tests/test_preview.py`.
+- `T-214-05`: actionable. Updated fallback payload example in `docs/approval_policy.md`.
+
+## Code Changes
+
+- `src/policy/approval_router.py`: `build_policy_preview(...)` now normalizes `approval_state` before passing it into the preview payload builder.
+- `src/policy/preview.py`: fallback payloads now retain `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` alongside `status="preview_unavailable"`.
