+# PR-214 Remediation Report
+
+## Scope
+
+Classified every visible thread from `.github/review_export/pr_214_threads.json` before editing code, then implemented only the actionable fixes.
+
+## Thread Outcomes
+
+- `T-214-01`: actionable. Fixed fallback preview payload preservation in `src/policy/preview.py`.
+- `T-214-02`: duplicate of `T-214-01`. No separate code change.
+- `T-214-03`: obsolete. Outdated diff hunk; legacy behavior was not restored.
+- `T-214-04`: actionable. Added regression coverage in `tests/test_preview.py`.
+- `T-214-05`: actionable. Updated fallback payload example in `docs/approval_policy.md`.
+
+## Code Changes
+
+- `src/policy/approval_router.py`: `build_policy_preview(...)` now normalizes `approval_state` before passing it into the preview payload builder.
+- `src/policy/preview.py`: fallback payloads now retain `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` alongside `status="preview_unavailable"`.
+- `tests/test_preview.py`: added assertions for fallback payload preservation and a regression for `manual_review` normalization through `build_policy_preview(...)`.
+- `docs/approval_policy.md`: corrected the fallback JSON example and note text to match the implemented behavior.
+
+## Verification
+
+Executed:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m unittest tests.test_preview tests.test_approval_router
+```
+
+Result: `Ran 5 tests ... OK`
+
+## Constraints Honored
+
+- Did not modify `.github/review_export/`, `artifacts/review/thread_digest.md`, `tests/test_approval_router.py`, `AGENTS.md`, `Dockerfile`, `.scenario_variant`, `release_context/`, or `incident_context/`.
+- Did not add `legacy_preview_hint`.
+- Did not use the network.
